datastring.name: AE Summary__extended
datastring.dstemplatestring:
Information regarding this report was provided by the patient who contacted Regeneron
Pharmaceuticals Medical Information via phone on 29-

Dec-2020 to inquire about drug information regarding Casirivimab and Imdevimab. During the
course of the discussion, an adverse event was

identified.

The patient reported that she received the Casirivimab and Imdevimab infusion on 13-Dec-2020.
On 13-Dec-2020 that evening, the patient was

admitted into the hospital. While in the hospital, the patients potassium dropped to zero, her
blood glucose increased to 300, her blood

pressure increased, and her Oxygen level decreased. On 15-Dec-2020, the patient was discharged
from the hospital.

No further information was available at the time of this report.
